  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Triple Combination Therapy With Dorzolamide Hydrochloride / Brimonidine Tartrate / Timolol Ophthalmic Solution in Patients With Glaucoma or Ocular Hypertension</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
