  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will investigate the safety and efficacy of Triple Combination Therapy with
      dorzolamide hydrochloride/brimonidine tartrate/timolol ophthalmic solution in patients with
      glaucoma or ocular hypertension who have elevated IOP on dorzolamide hydrochloride/timolol
      maleate combination therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
